Loss of life expectancy due to stroke and its subtypes in urban and rural areas 
in China, 2005-2020.

Wang Z(#)(1)(2), Liu W(#)(3), Ren Y(1)(2), Zhang C(1)(2), Yang J(1)(2), Wang 
L(3), Zhou M(3), Yin P(4), Hao J(5)(2), Ma Q(5)(2).

Author information:
(1)Department of Neurology, Xuanwu Hospital, Capital Medical University, 
