(2)National Center for Neurological Disorders, Beijing, China.
(3)National Center for Chronic and Non-communicable Disease Control and 
Prevention, Chinese Center for Disease Control and Prevention, Beijing, China.
(4)National Center for Chronic and Non-communicable Disease Control and 
Prevention, Chinese Center for Disease Control and Prevention, Beijing, China 
m.qingfeng@163.com yinpeng@ncncd.chinacdc.cn haojunwei@vip.163.com.
(5)Department of Neurology, Xuanwu Hospital, Capital Medical University, 
Beijing, China m.qingfeng@163.com yinpeng@ncncd.chinacdc.cn 
haojunwei@vip.163.com.
