[Human immunodeficiency virus and venous thromboembolism: Role of direct oral 
anticoagulants].

[Article in French]

Bentounes NK(1), Le Hingrat Q(2), Planquette B(3), Darnige L(1), Khider L(4), 
Sanchez O(3), Smadja DM(5), Mauge L(6), Lê MP(7), Mirault T(8), Gendron N(9).

